spec_data.Name: texlive-pst-electricfield
spec_data.Description:
The package provides macros to plot electric field and
equipotential lines using PStricks. There may be any number of
charges which can be placed in a cartesian coordinate system by
(x,y) values.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Sun 06 Aug 2017 07:51:33 AM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Draw electric field and equipotential lines with PStricks
